"✓ AOI split successfully! Generated %(task_count)s task areas using "
"%(algorithm)s."
msgstr ""
"✓ E kewara AOI nke ọma! E mepụtara mpaghara ọrụ %(task_count)s site na "
"iji %(algorithm)s."

#: app/htmx/setup_step_routes.py:460
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Previewing %(task_count)s task boundaries%(data_extract_info)s. Review "
"the results below. If satisfied, click \"Accept Task Choices\" to save. "
"Otherwise, adjust parameters above and click \"Split Again\" to "
"regenerate."
msgstr ""
"A na-elele ókè ọrụ %(task_count)s%(data_extract_info)s. Nyochaa nsonaazụ "
"ndị dị n'okpuru. Ọ bụrụ na afọ juru gị, pịa \"Accept Task Choices\" iji "
"chekwaa. Ma ọ bụghị ya, gbanwee paramita ndị dị n'elu ma pịa \"Split "
"Again\" iji mepụta ọzọ."

