"Ndị njikwa ọrụ na-eji Field-TM hazie ọrụ maapụ, kọwaa mpaghara mmasị, "
"mepụta fọm nyocha, ma kewaa ọrụ n'ime ọrụ a pụrụ ijikwa."

#: app/templates/landing.html:633
msgid "Define a project area and upload or choose a survey form"
